data.description: Cute 3 bed, 2 bath, 1542 sq. ft. home is just moments away from Benton Schools, restaurants, and shopping. Fresh paint throughout the house. The master bath has a large jetted soaking tub, and a brand new walk-in shower. The spacious kitchen has all stainless appliances and a pantry. Situated on a Cul-De-Sac lot giving you plenty of space. The backyard has space for entertaining or simply unwinding. With all the city services readily available, convenience is your new neighbor. The large lot ensures you won't feel encroached upon by neighbors, granting you that sought-after peace and privacy. Your new chapter starts here. Make this charming home yours and embrace a life of comfort, and convenience. Don't miss out on this great home! *** Agents See Remarks *** See it now - 3D Tour *** https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=tZWmhBjVQNf
